cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CE, cs.HC 

The paper presents a window opening model for commercial buildings using deep learning methods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the practical potential of the proposed model by incorporating it in the Modelica-based thermal building simulation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). The study involves evaluating the model using data from occupants from an office building, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
